Bola Bamigbola, Osogbo. Three Chinese miners abducted in Ijoka village near Itagunmodi, Osun State, on Monday have been released. The three men regained freedom on Wednesday. Although details of how they were freed was not available as of the time of filing this report, the Osun State Police Commissioner, Abiodun Ige, however, confirmed their release in a chat with our correspondent. Details laterâ€¦